        </ul>
        <p>Reducing - Try to reduce the amount of waste you produce, as this is the best way to help the environment! If you cannot avoid producing the waste, try…</p>
        <p class="btmspace-30">Avoid giving presents with excess packaging.Consider using doorstep delivery services for organic vegetables, milk and other fresh produce - goods often come in little or returnable packaging.</p>
        <!-- <footer class="nospace"><a class="btn" href="#">Know more &raquo;</a></footer> -->
