        </ul> -->
        <p>Recycling (and composting)
          This enables the materials you throw away to be used again by making them into new products.</p>
        <p class="btmspace-30">At the garden centre look for products that are made from recycled materials such as plant pots, containers and garden benches made from recycled plastic, recycled paper liners for hanging baskets and compost and soil conditioners made from recycled organic materials.</p>
        <!-- <footer class="nospace"><a class="btn" href="#">Know more &raquo;</a></footer> -->
      </div>
